    "form_header_text": "FY 2027 VA-04 Programmatic Appropriations Request Form",
    "form_instructions_text": "Thank you for your interest in placing a programmatic request with Congresswoman Jennifer McClellan. Please ensure that the information provides is accurate and complete to ensure a thorough review. Submissions made after this deadline may not be considered and a submission does not guarantee funding by the Appropriations Committee. Please note that programmatic requests are different from community project funding requests and therefore require a different form and review process. An example of a programmatic request would be an increase in funding to the Environmental Protection Agency's Chesapeake Bay Program. Whereas, a community project funding request would be to support funding to a Virginia institution of higher education to study the impact of sea level rise in the Chesapeake Bay and the impact it has on the estuary's ecosystem. Please contact the Congresswoman's office at 202-225-6365 if you have any questions about submitting a request.",
